{"tid":742030,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"覺唔覺得政府應該將監獄嘅cctv擺喺港台度播?","createTime":"2018-07-14T07:59:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-14T08:17:37.000Z","uid":41317,"like":9,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"91aef8fd97aae64680c52a6ab5d49be7317466f7","tid":742030,"uid":41317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T07:59:39.000Z","msg":"香港人最鍾意睇人仆街望人坐監<br />\n如果可以長期俾香港人睇住一班人折墜<br />\n一定可以成為一個發洩點減低民怨<br />\n<br />\n啲監犯喺入面做生做死都係得嗰一個幾毫收入<br />\n如果可以將個每個倉嘅cctv當直播咁做<br />\n將啲donate當糧咁出返俾啲犯<br />\n一嚟可以提升收入, 二嚟又可以加強同倉嘅團結性<br />\n有錢搵仲邊會掛住打生打死<br />\n<br />\n政府又可以喺啲donate度抽水創造另類稅收<br />\n<br />\n你話係咪winwinwin三贏先?"},{"pid":"311c92f60c4243f291bc79047e056b0170299344","tid":742030,"uid":30347,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T08:04:17.000Z","msg":"ATV 魚樂無窮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cde7560e6a56e68e9c8e1390ceb588994bf346d0","tid":742030,"uid":125333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T08:05:56.000Z","msg":"你都悶啦"},{"pid":"2b46d92d7144e9375859d4c0e0af3540149e0df3","tid":742030,"uid":41317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cde7560e6a56e68e9c8e1390ceb588994bf346d0","tid":742030,"uid":125333,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T08:05:56.000Z","msg":"你都悶啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T08:09:56.000Z","msg":"人都係鍾意偷窺<br />\n只要倉入面嗰班係活人<br />\n佢地就唔會覺得冇野睇, 佢地只係會覺得未有野睇<br />\n然後一路mon住"},{"pid":"50cec088e0b3a728f159ccc0a1f57fe20219ecb0","tid":742030,"uid":16676,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-14T08:14:01.000Z","msg":"掂嘅話美國一早做左啦<br />\n口講有人權<br />\n一陣比人用唇語，摩斯密碼與外邊通訊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n策劃逃獄或者世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/saudi_arabia.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/nigeria.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fifa/tunisia.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/ass